text: This is I.N back with Pong Dang Log.
It's been a couple of years
since I've been on a family trip.
And I'm back with another Pong Dang Log.
I'll have a fun time here.
What's there to be embarrassed about?
[(I stayed in the heated pool because it was cold)]
Should we go in this one?
I think we can go in this one.
[(I decided to go in the regular pool with my brother)]
[(Failed to find a nickname)] The PD for the day.
I'm enjoying the Yeosu night sea.
You need to ask me questions like in an interview.
I ate a bowl and a half of rice!
[(Forcing my brother to ask)] No more questions?
[(Even the wind was nice)] It's really windy.
[(The PD for the day quickly turned into the little brother)]
[(Being Baby Bread's family is an extreme job)] -I don't know. -You think you can do it?
No, I'm not going to do it.
[(Yoon has no interest in me...)] -I don't have one. -None?
What are you going to do tomorrow?
[(Ta-da! I'm here to have fun as planned)]
[(I went on a zipline and it was so fun)]
[(Was I scared? A bit, but it was fun!)]
I'm here to ride a cable car!
Don't play music. It'll get copyright claimed.
[(My family's really looking out for my vlog)] -Really? -Yeah, it'll get claimed.
[(We rode a crystal cable car that had a transparent floor)]
[(It was so nice that it was sunny)]
Yesterday I bought a Gundam at the store
so I'm going to assemble it.
I wanted to make it yesterday
but I fell asleep after eating.
[(My older brother and Yoon made theirs already...)]
It's been a while since I've assembled one of these.
You saying that is going to be permanently recorded on this vlog.
[(My mom's flustered)] -Lee Junho's still in JYP, right? -Yes.
[(Observing the Gundam my brothers made)] This is the one your older brother made.
[(Need to make it better than Yoon's!)] Yoon said putting on the stickers was hard.
I should've put the stickers on while assembling it.
[(Putting on the stickers really is hard)]
[(The Gundam and stickers are so small but my hands are too big)] I'm going to act like a nice kid.
[(My family's more conscious of the vlog than me...)]
I need to tell them to edit this part out.
[(Need to be real, diligent, and humble)]
[(I was so happy to complete this I shot this in slow motion)]
I wanted to record a lot
because I was hanging out with my family.
[(I'll just record more in Busan!)] It'll be fine, right?
[(My mom turned off the lights thinking no one was inside)] -Who's there? -Me.
[(The youngest in SKZ, but second at home)]
I look so scary right now...
I'll come back after a shower.
[(Always need to put on toner and lotion before bed)]
My hair's long, so it won't dry.
My birthday meal my mom prepared!
[(My mom's such a good cook... I ate two bowls)] Eating this soup might clear up your stomach.
[(A heart-shaped strawberry... So cool)] What is this?
How is a strawberry shaped like this?
[(Like a croissant! Showing STAY because it's so cool)] I'm specially giving this to you.
but my parents can't celebrate it with me,
[(An early birthday party, though it's in a few days)] so in advance...
[(So mean)] -No, I'm not going to sing. -Why not?
[(At least my mom sang)] Happy birthday our dear son.
[(It's probably the same as what STAY think!)]
